制作方称该剧是正剧，拒绝虚假、雷人的抗日剧。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.qq.com/a/20130726/007757.htm |title=《战火中的花蕾》历史成新宠 拒绝雷人抗战剧 |date=2013-07-26 |accessdate=2013-07-29 |work=腾讯网 |archive-date=2019-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130163001/https://ent.qq.com/a/20130726/007757.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

